data.description: HORSE PROPERTY!!! Gorgeous property on 5.00 ACRES, 15 minutes from Lewiston. Single level home with a bonus room above the garage. Home features vaulted ceilings, open concept, large master bedroom, oversized garage, & tons of character. Interior was just painted, new flooring, new counter tops, & new light fixtures are some of the recent updates. Bonus above the garage could be used as a 4th bedroom or playroom. SELLER WILL GIVE EXTERIOR PAINT CREDIT & is working on replacing several windows!! Massive 40x60 SHOP.  Pasuture areas are fenced for livestock. RV hook-up (water/power).  Sprinkler system throughout the yard surrounding the home. This home is a must see if you are considering your own hobby farm or have horses needing some space.
